🧑‍💻 Abhishek Kasaudhan — Developer Portfolio


Personal portfolio website of Abhishek Kasaudhan, a Full-Stack Developer & AI/ML Engineer based in Lucknow, India. Built to showcase real production projects, technical skills, and professional background to recruiters and hiring teams.



🔗 Live Site: https://www.abhishektech.me/


✨ Features


🌙 Dark luxury theme — deep charcoal background with warm cream text and teal-blue gradient accents
🔤 Typed.js role rotator — animated headline cycling through MERN Stack, Full-Stack, and AI/ML roles
📊 Animated skill bars — scroll-triggered progress indicators for each technical skill
🔢 Animated stat counters — production projects, CGPA, core technologies, graduation year
🃏 Project cards — banner images, tech stack chips, live demo and GitHub CTA links
🗂️ Education timeline — degree, institution, CGPA, and key achievements
📬 Working contact form — powered by Formspree with AJAX submit and success/error states
📍 Active nav highlight — nav link underlines as you scroll through sections
🔝 Back to top button — appears after scrolling, smooth scroll back
📱 Fully responsive — mobile (320px+), tablet, laptop, and desktop layouts
♿ Accessible — semantic HTML, ARIA labels, visible focus states, prefers-reduced-motion support



🛠️ Tech Stack

LayerTechnologiesMarkupHTML5 (semantic elements, ARIA attributes)StylingCSS3 (Custom Properties, Flexbox, Grid, Glassmorphism, Animations)TypographyGoogle Fonts — PoppinsJavaScriptVanilla JS (Intersection Observer, fetch API, scroll events)LibrariesTyped.js, ScrollRevealForm BackendFormspree (AJAX)DeploymentGitHub Pages / Netlify


📁 Project Structure

