💼 Featured Projects

🏋️ AI Personal Health Assistant

Final-year React Native mobile app delivering personalized 6-day workout plans. Built with Node.js/Express REST APIs, JWT authentication, and MongoDB. Documented with Postman and Swagger.

✈️ TripNow — AI Travel Planner

Full-stack AI-powered travel platform with itinerary generation, real-time weather integration, PDF export, and cloud deployment.
