📦 Running Locally

No build tools or dependencies required — just open in a browser.

bashgit clone https://github.com/abhishekkasaudhan45/Abhishek-Portfolio
cd portfolio
# Open index.html in your browser
# Or use VS Code Live Server for hot reload


